Package popt4jlib.LocalSearch

Local Search algorithms parallel implementation for combinatorial optimization problems.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IntSetNeighborhoodFilterIntf extension of NeighborhoodFilterIntf class to work specifically with Set<Integer> arg solutions and Integers as "guides".
NeighborhoodFilterIntf specifies filters for determining "trial" points in the neighborhood of a solution arg, using a "guide" x.
 

Class Summary
DLS class implements a parallel LocalSearch method for combinatorial optimization problems, obeying the general OptimizerIntf contract.
IntSetN1AllMovesMaker the class implements the notion of the N_1 neighborhood of a set of integers.
IntSetN21AllMovesMaker the class implements the notion of the N_{2+1} neighborhood of a set of integers.
IntSetN2AllMovesMaker the class implements the notion of the N_2 neighborhood of a set of integers.
IntSetN2RXPAllMovesMaker the class implements the notion of the N_{-2+P} neighborhood of a set of integers.
 

Exception Summary
LocalSearchException encapsulates exceptions that a Local-Search algorithm may throw.
 

Package popt4jlib.LocalSearch Description

Local Search algorithms parallel implementation for combinatorial optimization problems.
